### Submit a transaction (via gateway)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transactions
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: demo-key-001

{
  "accountId": "acct-42",
  "amount": 250.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "region": "US-EAST",
  "type": "PAYMENT"
}

### Replay the same Idempotency-Key -> expect 409 DUPLICATE
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transactions
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: demo-key-001

{
  "accountId": "acct-42",
  "amount": 250.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "region": "US-EAST",
  "type": "PAYMENT"
}

### Query state (replace {id} with transactionId from the 202 response)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/transactions/{id}
